      "content": "it’s more than just being sad. it’s like... the essence of who i was is just gone. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person staring back. if the art was the only thing that made me real, then what am i now? just a biological accident? it feels so pointless to just keep going when the core of me is dead.",
