      "content": "but that's just it... the person you're telling me to reach out to... that person doesn't exist anymore. the \"me\" that was worth holding hands with is gone. if the soul of the artist is dead, then what is left? just this heavy, breathing machine that takes up space and consumes resources. it feels like I'm just a ghost haunting a body that doesn't even belong to me anymore.",
